        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "These voice contrasts are maintained even in songs where they collaborate. They signal different sonic lineages. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
